messages.content: What is the purpose of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator in ComfyUI?
The Advanced Sequence Seed Generator in ComfyUI is a custom node that generates seeds based on special number sequences.
Which number sequences are supported by the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator?
The Advanced Sequence Seed Generator supports Fibonacci, Prime, Padovan, Triangular, Catalan, Pell, and Lucas number sequences.
Is there a visual representation of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator node available?
Yes, there is a screenshot of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator node provided in the documentation.
How can one support the author of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator?
One can support the author of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator by making a small donation via the provided Ko-fi link.
Where can one purchase workflows created by the author of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator?
Workflows created by the author of the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator can be purchased on their website, stefanoflore.it.
Is the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator a standalone application or a plugin?
The Advanced Sequence Seed Generator is a custom node for ComfyUI, not a standalone application.
What is the author's website for the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator?
The author's website for the Advanced Sequence Seed Generator is stefanoflore.it.
